format/configuration/README.md
     1Рєњ# Configuration
     3РєњThis section details the configuration options available in the ***book.toml***:
     4Рєњ- **[General]** configuration including the `book`, `rust`, `build` sections
     5Рєњ- **[Preprocessor]** configuration for default and custom book preprocessors
     6Рєњ- **[Renderer]** configuration for the HTML, Markdown and custom renderers
     7Рєњ- **[Environment Variable]** configuration for overriding configuration options in your environment
     8Рєњ
     9Рєњ[General]: general.md
    10Рєњ[Preprocessor]: preprocessors.md
    11Рєњ[Renderer]: renderers.md
    12Рєњ[Environment Variable]: environment-variables.md
